From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|orchis|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ὄρχις||orchid, testicle|lang=grc}} (ostensibly from the shape of the roots<ref>{{R:LSJ|o)/rxis}}</ref>).

